{
  "tag": "layout-fit",
  "className": "padding10 h100 overflow-auto",
  "initStore": {
    "apiList": [
      {
        "code": "tag",
        "name": "table",
        "type": "string",
        "description": "页面级布局标签"
      },
      {
        "code": "initStore",
        "name": "初始化store",
        "type": "dict",
        "description": "通过定义和绑定数据。定义 dataList: [] 作为数据源，并通过模板字符串 rowData: '${dataList}' 将该数组绑定至表格的行数据属性，以此实现表格内容的动态更新与用户交互。"
      },
      {
        "code": "initAction",
        "name": "初始化动作",
        "type": "array[action]",
        "description": "页面初始化时。通过请求更新全局状态并创建可复用的分组动作，以模块化方式高效管理数据获取与分组逻辑。可以设置group,以便reload-group-action调用"
      },
      {
        "code": "title",
        "name": "页面标题",
        "type": "string",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "code": "topRight",
        "name": "右侧工具栏",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": "页面右侧工具栏，一般放新增、修改、删除"
      },
      {
        "code": "searchToolBar",
        "name": "搜索栏",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": "页面顶部搜索栏，一般放表单"
      },
      {
        "code": "searchBarRight",
        "name": "搜索栏右侧",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": "页面顶部搜索栏右侧，一般固定放一下搜索，操作栏等"
      },
      {
        "code": "children",
        "name": "主体内容区域",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": ""
      },
      {
        "code": "bottomToolBar",
        "name": "底部区域",
        "type": "array[configNode]",
        "description": "一般放分页"
      }
    ]
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "tag": "h1",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "table示例"
    },
    {
      "tag": "label",
      "className": "padding-left10 padding-bottom10",
      "children": [
        "标签 tag=table 作为 ag-Grid 组件的继承者，不仅支持 ag-Grid 的所有属性，还提供了灵活的自定义列展示功能，使用户能够根据需求定制表格的显示效果。",
        {
          "tag": "a",
          "target": "_blank",
          "href": "https://www.ag-grid.com/react-data-grid/getting-started/",
          "children": "查看ag-grid文档"
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "li",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "strong",
                  "children": "功能描述"
                },
                "：tag=table 标签继承了 ag-Grid 组件的强大功能，包括数据排序、筛选、分页等，同时允许用户通过自定义列配置，灵活地控制表格中各列的显示方式和顺序。"
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "li",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "strong",
                  "children": "使用方法"
                },
                "：用户可以在 tag=table 标签中定义列属性，通过设置 field、headerName、width、cellRenderer 等参数，实现对列的个性化展示。"
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "li",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "strong",
                  "children": "应用场景"
                },
                "：此功能适用于需要高度定制表格显示的应用程序，如数据报表、复杂的数据管理系统等，通过 tag=table 标签，可以构建出既强大又灵活的表格组件。"
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 12,
          "style": {
            "height": "400px",
            "overflow": "auto"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "h3",
              "children": "代码配置示例",
              "className": "border-bottom"
            },
            {
              "tag": "coder",
              "language": "json",
              "value": {
                "tag": "table",
                "selection": "${selection}",
                "rowSelection": "multiple",
                "rowData": "${dataList}",
                "columnDefs": [
                  {
                    "headerName": "#",
                    "width": 60,
                    "valueGetter": "node.rowIndex + 1",
                    "sortable": false,
                    "suppressSizeToFit": true,
                    "pinned": "left"
                  },
                  {
                    "pinned": "left",
                    "checkboxSelection": true,
                    "headerCheckboxSelection": true,
                    "headerName": "账号",
                    "field": "username"
                  },
                  {
                    "headerName": "工号",
                    "field": "work_code"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 12,
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "h3",
              "children": "配置简述",
              "className": "border-bottom"
            },
            {
              "tag": "ol",
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "tag=table-表格"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "selection-选中的绑定对象"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "rowData-行数据"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "rowSelection-选中模式"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": "columnDefs-表头"
                },
                {
                  "tag": "li",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "tag": "a",
                      "target": "_blank",
                      "href": "https://www.ag-grid.com/react-data-grid/getting-started/",
                      "children": "查看ag-grid文档"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "h3",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "API（注意：configNode表示低代码配置，action表示动作配置）"
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [
        {
          "tag": "layout-fit",
          "style": {
            "height": "350px",
            "width": "100%"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "table",
              "rowData": "${apiList}",
              "tooltipShowDelay": 0,
              "columnDefs": [
                {
                  "headerName": "#",
                  "width": 60,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true,
                  "valueGetter": "node.rowIndex + 1",
                  "sortable": false,
                  "pinned": "left"
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "字段",
                  "field": "code",
                  "width": 150,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "名称",
                  "field": "name",
                  "width": 150,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "类型",
                  "field": "type",
                  "width": 150,
                  "suppressSizeToFit": true
                },
                {
                  "headerName": "描述",
                  "field": "description",
                  "tooltipField": "description"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tag": "h3",
      "className": "border-bottom",
      "children": "展示示例"
    },
    {
      "tag": "row",
      "children": [
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 8,
          "style": {
            "height": "500px"
          },
          "className": "padding10",
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "label",
              "className": "bold",
              "children": "基础显示"
            },
            {
              "tag": "coder-preview",
              "coder": {
                "tag": "layout-fit",
                "className": "border",
                "title": "页面标题",
                "topRight": [
                  "顶部右侧工具栏"
                ],
                "searchToolBar": [
                  "搜索区域"
                ],
                "searchBarRight": [
                  "搜索右侧区域"
                ],
                "children": [
                  "内容区域"
                ],
                "bottomToolBar": [
                  "底部区域"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "col",
          "span": 16,
          "style": {
            "height": "500px"
          },
          "className": "padding10",
          "children": [
            {
              "tag": "label",
              "className": "bold",
              "children": "增删改查"
            },
            {
              "tag": "coder-preview",
              "coder": {
                "tag": "layout-fit",
                "className": "border",
                "title": "用户管理",
                "initStore": {
                  "selection": [],
                  "dataList": [
                    {
                      "username": "zz",
                      "nick": "张三"
                    },
                    {
                      "username": "ls",
                      "nick": "李四"
                    }
                  ],
                  "searchForm": {
                    "search": "",
                    "page": 1,
                    "size": 10
                  },
                  "count": 101
                },
                "topRight": [
                  {
                    "tag": "button",
                    "type": "primary",
                    "icon": "FaPlus",
                    "children": "新增"
                  },
                  {
                    "tag": "button",
                    "children": "编辑",
                    "disabled": "${selection.length !=1 }",
                    "icon": "FaPencilAlt"
                  },
                  {
                    "tag": "button",
                    "disabled": "${selection.length <=0 }",
                    "type": "primary",
                    "confirm": {
                      "title": "确认删除吗？",
                      "description": "${'确认删除【'+selection.map(item=>item.nick+'（'+item.username+'）').join(',')+'】'+selection.length+'记录吗？'}"
                    },
                    "danger": true,
                    "children": "删除",
                    "icon": "FaTrashAlt"
                  }
                ],
                "searchToolBar": [
                  {
                    "tag": "form",
                    "name": "user-form",
                    "initialValues": "${searchForm}",
                    "labelCol": {
                      "span": 4
                    },
                    "wrapperCol": {
                      "span": 19
                    },
                    "submitOnChange": true,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "tag": "row",
                        "children": [
                          {
                            "tag": "col",
                            "span": 10,
                            "children": [
                              {
                                "tag": "form-item",
                                "name": "search",
                                "label": "搜索",
                                "children": [
                                  {
                                    "tag": "input",
                                    "placeholder": "账号/用户名",
                                    "allowClear": true
                                  }
                                ]
                              }
                            ]
                          },
                          {
                            "tag": "col",
                            "span": 10,
                            "children": [
                              {
                                "tag": "button",
                                "type": "primary",
                                "children": "搜索",
                                "icon": "FaSearch"
                              },
                              {
                                "tag": "button",
                                "action": [
                                  {
                                    "tag": "reset-form",
                                    "formName": "user-form"
                                  }
                                ],
                                "icon": "FaUndo",
                                "children": "重置"
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        ]
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ],
                "children": [
                  {
                    "tag": "table",
                    "selection": "${selection}",
                    "rowSelection": "multiple",
                    "rowData": "${dataList}",
                    "columnDefs": [
                      {
                        "headerName": "#",
                        "width": 60,
                        "suppressSizeToFit": true,
                        "valueGetter": "node.rowIndex + 1",
                        "sortable": false,
                        "pinned": "left"
                      },
                      {
                        "pinned": "left",
                        "checkboxSelection": true,
                        "headerCheckboxSelection": true,
                        "headerName": "账号",
                        "field": "username"
                      },
                      {
                        "headerName": "昵称",
                        "field": "nick"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ],
                "bottomToolBar": [
                  {
                    "tag": "pagination",
                    "showSizeChanger": true,
                    "align": "right",
                    "pageSize": "${searchForm.size}",
                    "current": "${searchForm.page}",
                    "total": "${count}",
                    "showTotal": true
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}